罩再融入人群，係更加好難指証你</strong></span>。<br />\n如果你無同police對抽，多數告你參與非法集結，而<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>你如果有戴口罩，更加認唔到你，官冇可能係無合理疑點下話個個係你</strong></span>。&quot;"},{"pid":"a244e2e7f1531a47f9e65b863c37c0dcd216a702","tid":1318871,"uid":149607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8efc86a526cdcb22be762731026ba55b6313f9d3","tid":1318871,"uid":227968,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T04:50:34.000Z","msg":"⼃<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G3PUUZH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG3PUUZH.png&h=c14f14c0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cNUYCc2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcNUYCc2.png&h=ef541050&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z7qkQx2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ7qkQx2.png&h=b14a42eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n和理非保護好自己"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T04:55:15.000Z","msg":"買大媽泳衣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dd44b1fd0af55f35607712301454017fb0ed3ea","tid":1318871,"uid":96897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T04:56:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"76df46e37e1e56a8a104fd94b4702c069a363126","tid":1318871,"uid":90521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae6abde89cc9287f4a95d2923608780a87f94d13","tid":1318871,"uid":2772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6242dd5839e3008622e533e9fe016dbc899a2653","tid":1318871,"uid":71606,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"dfc9c8ffba5a331d8f39271add8379df1b4f4020","tid":1318871,"uid":2772,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T04:48:15.000Z","msg":"其實有冇得資助物資組"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T04:49:38.000Z","msg":"自己買定之後放去物資站"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T04:52:21.000Z","msg":"你啱<br />\n<br />\n我搵搵係邊<br />\n同有咩窿路睇下要咩物資同有咩太多"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T04:56:58.000Z","msg":"你前線聽得叫要咩最多未知缺咩